data.title: Iron Maiden: The Clairvoyant (Music Video 1988)
data.meta_description: Iron Maiden: The Clairvoyant: Directed by Toby Phillips. With Iron Maiden, Bruce Dickinson, Steve Harris, Nicko McBrain. Iron Maiden performs in the music video "The Clairvoyant" from the album "Seventh Son of a Seventh Son" recorded for EMI Records. The music video features the band performing live on stage at the 1988 Monsters of Rock festival in Donington Park in England.
